[SN]TITLE[SN]
£170k Ferrari crashes in icy conditions in Cardiff

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A £170,000 sports car has crashed into a pillar in icy conditions in Cardiff.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
South Wales Police said the Ferrari 458 Italia crashed in Llandennis Avenue, Cyncoed, on Friday morning.
Most of Wales has been subject to a "be aware" snow and ice warning since Thursday.
The force said no-one was injured.
